  "text": "Proof: Because * \u222a * * = * = * * is a weak order, is a semiorder. Besides, * = * * is continuous because * is lower semicontinuous and * * is upper semicontinuous (cf., Bosi et al. [CITATION_1] , proof of implication (ii) \u21d2 (iii) in Theorem 3). Now Theorem 1 applies. \u00a1 Corollary 1 contains the following widely known specification.",
